
1.8     2025-07-14    lichtkind
-------
    * = major feature release
    * * added support of 5 color spaces: NCol YUV CIELUV CIELCHab CIELCHuv,
                                 rewrote CIEXYZ CIELAB
    * + extended range definitions with explicit type names
    * + color spaces can now define value procision,
                                    value suffix ('%') and
                                    value parsing regex
    * ? added documentation for color space object and missing formats
    * & moved code into Space::Format space attr object class
    * & removed Carp and Test::Warn as dependencies
    * & moved color set function into own package
    * ~ renamed blend method to mix
    * ~ default space of methods 'distance', 'mix' and 'gradient'
        went from HSL to RGB, consistent with Space::Hub defaults (complement has to be HSL)

